The paper deals with obstacle avoidance in UAVs, which is a topic closely related to robotics and control systems. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses deep reinforcement learning and recurrent neural networks, which are techniques commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
